The paper proposes a new graph embedding technique that aims to simplify and speed up data analysis tasks involving graph representation learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR). However, since the paper focuses on graph embedding and community detection, which are common topics in the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category, this is the most likely category. The other categories are also possible because the paper involves machine learning, data structures and algorithms, and information retrieval.
